title: IGT Slots: Diamond Galaxy [PC + Mac]

Description
Enjoy a new set of actual casino slots from the world's leading slot machine manufacturer, IGT!

Get the latest collection of IGT's most popular slot machines, including 5-reel video machines -- complete with second-screen bonus rounds and Free Games bonus features -- plus classic 3-reel spinners. Tour the 3D casino and find famous, big-name video machines like Diamond Galaxy, Pharaoh's Fortune, Fire Horse, Duck Stamps, Buffet Mania, Kingpin Bowling and more. Or try your hand at a number of casino classics like Triple Triple Diamond, 5 Times Pay, Wild Cherry... plus others.

Bring all the fun and excitement of the real casino experience right to your own computer. Machines offer a variety of different denominations, from $0.01 all the way up to $100! You can play single-line or multi-line wagers: up to 100-line wagers per spin! Or try out a variety of MultiWay slot machines with 243, 720 and 1024 ways to win! And choose from 2 modes of gameplay: get the realistic Vegas experience with True Casino Payouts, or live the Vegas fantasy with Extra High Payouts.
